$.toast({
    heading: 'Information',
    text: 'Now you can add icons to generate different kinds of toasts',
    showHideTransition: 'slide',
    position:'top-right',
    icon: 'info'
})

icon常用：info、error、warning、success
showHideTransition常用：fade、slide
position常用：
bottom-left
bottom-right
bottom-center
top-right
top-left
top-center
mid-center
文档：http://kamranahmed.info/toast#